 st measure of economic growth and helps traders judge whether the econom
 y is accelerating or slowing.\n\n• Frequency: Quarterly\, with revisio
 ns.\n\n• Notes: GDP can be backward-looking\, so markets often react m
 ore strongly when the result changes the outlook for central-bank policy
