DTEND:20260916T193000Z
SUMMARY:🔥 US Fed: FOMC Press Conference
DESCRIPTION:Source: US Fed\nImpact: high\nOfficial Federal Reserve monthl
 y calendar FOMC press conference entry.\nExplainer:\n• What it is: Cen
 tral Bank Rate Decision\n\n• Measures: Interest-rate decision\, policy
  statement and guidance from the central bank.\n\n• Usual market effec
 t: More hawkish-than-expected guidance is usually bullish for the local 
 currency and bearish for bonds. More dovish-than-expected guidance is us
 ually bearish for the currency and bullish for bonds.\n\n• Why traders
  care: Central-bank decisions directly affect interest rates\, currency 
 valuation\, bond yields and equity risk appetite.\n\n• Frequency: Sche
 duled several times per year.\n\n• Notes: The market often reacts not 
 only to the rate decision\, but also to the statement\, forecasts\, pres
 s conference and tone.\n\n• Acronyms: FOMC = Federal Open Market Commi
 ttee\; RBA = Reserve Bank of Australia.\nOfficial source: https://www.fe
 deralreserve.gov/newsevents/2026-september.htm
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.federalreserve.gov/newsevents/2026-september.htm
